  "text": "where \u03be \u2208 C is a spectral parameter and m = \u00b5(u) \u2212 u xx . Similar to the \u00b5CH equation, the \u00b5DP equation also admits bi-Hamiltonian structure and infinite hierarchy of conservation laws, and it is formally integrable [CITATION_1] . The first few conservation laws in the hierarchy ar\u1ebd",
